Name of the Vacancies:

  • Inspector, Tax Asst & MTS

Description

Latest Central; Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by Income Tax Department for Inspector vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Inspector, from 08-07-2021, and till 25-08-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an Inspector in Income Tax Department, Income Tax Department, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 25-08-2021 by 23:59 Hrs

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 345 years old. 

Income Tax Department Inspector Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Income Tax Department Inspector, Tax Asst & MTS Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Inspector. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of the Income Tax Department and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Income Tax Department
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
